reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater chic and high-quality, appreciating its smooth texture and comfortable, non-itchy feel.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cozy quality
items.body: I adore this sweater. It is oversized so I did size down. The texture is soft, warm and good quality. I love the cut and shape. I have the apricot stripes and just ordered the solid purple one for Christmas. Read more
items.author: Paula Elks

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft, oversized on trend
items.body: Over this. Oversized and soft. Good quality. Good finish to seams. Stylish with black jeans and sneakers or booties. Read more
items.author: P. Wright

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Butter soft and high quality
items.body: Very high quality, and extremely soft. This sweater has extreme versatility as it is warm itself but also thin enough to fit a jacket over. Stretchy material so it is very comfortable. Length is great and with the slits in the sides I was able to tuck the front up while leaving the back down. Cost was very doable and color was exactly what I expected! Read more
items.author: Elijah

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love this Sweater but not on Me.
items.body: This is a really nice seater. It is thick, well made, good quality and a beautiful color combination that looks great with faded jeans. The sweater is warm and loose, it came to the bottom of my hips in length. The neckline is a crew neck and unfortunately to neck was too loose on me. I wish the neckline was a mock and I would have kept this sweater in a heartbeat. It is TTS, but I didn’t wash it so I cannot attest to shrinkage. Read more
items.author: sailfishes

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very cute
items.body: Who doesn't need another cute oversized sweater?? The material is good quality, soft. Doesn't feel cheap. Fit is good - probably could have sized down even but the small still looks good. Not see thru and not itchy at all. Probably will get in other colors. Read more
items.author: Sarah

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars One Of My New Favorite Wardrobe Pieces
items.body: I received the ETCYY Oversized Sweater for Women as a gift, and I couldn't be happier with it! The quality of the material is fantastic—it's soft, cozy, and incredibly comfortable to wear. The oversized fit is stylish and flattering, making it perfect for layering or wearing on its own. I love the versatility of this sweater. It's great for casual days out, lounging at home, or even dressing up for a night out. The color is beautiful and true to the picture, and the stitching is well-done, ensuring durability for long-term wear. Overall, I'm thrilled with this gift and would highly recommend the ETCYY Oversized Sweater to anyone looking for a stylish and comfortable addition to their wardrobe. It's quickly become one of my favorite pieces, and I can't wait to wear it all season long! Read more
items.author: Anna O'Neal

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not oversized
items.body: This is a super comfy and soft sweater but it doesn’t fit the way the image shows. I ordered my true to size and it’s not an oversized sweater. If you want oversized definitely size up! It is really nicely made though! Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fabulous
items.body: This sweater is amazing! Quality material , soft and just really classy looking. I’m 5’3 and 144 lbs and I got a medium. It’s roomy and I love the oversized look. Read more
items.author: DL Paradis

short_description:
Womens Dress is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

long_description:
Womens Dress is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Print Red, Pure Dark Pink, Stripe Black, Pure Gray Green, Print Blue, Stripe Khaki, Stripe Apricot, Plain Green, Pure Purple, Plain Apricot, Plain Coffee, Stripe Army Green, Leaf Green, Pure Black. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
